OL,6,FHis son John heads up the Football
OL,7,FFamilies for Justice (FFJ) group which
OL,8,Fis calling on the football authorities
OL,9,Fto do more to help former players
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with dementia - which he
OL,11,Fsays "killed" his father.
OL,13,FThe Football Brain Health Fund was set
OL,14,Fup in 2023 by the Professional
OL,15,FFootballers' Association (PFA) and the
OL,16,FPremier League with an initial
OL,17,F#1million available to support ex-
OL,18,Fplayers and families with care costs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'R(,,,,,,,,,
