OL,3,CNobby Stiles 'sold medals to pay for
OL,4,Cdementia care'
OL,6,FBut John says the fund is not nearly
OL,7,Fenough, with his father forced to sell
OL,8,Fmedals earned during his playing
OL,9,Fcareer to fund his care.
OL,11,FJohn, a group of former players,
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham,
OL,13,Fand Liverpool City Region Mayor Steve
OL,14,FRotheram met in Manchester to discuss
OL,15,Fways to impose political pressure on
OL,16,Fthe football authorities to do more.
OL,18,FPeter Reid was among several high
OL,19,Fprofile former players who have thrown
OL,20,Ftheir weight behind the campaign.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
