OL,3,CNobby Stiles 'sold medals to pay for
OL,4,Cdementia care'
OL,6,FAmong them was football manager,
OL,7,Fpundit and former player Peter Reid,
OL,8,Fwho says he has lost friends, who were
OL,9,Ffootballers, over the years to
OL,10,Fdementia and that their families
OL,11,F"struggled".
OL,13,FHe added: "I think the only real help
OL,14,Fis the PFA #1 million fund and it's
OL,15,Fnot enough. We have got help these
OL,16,Ffamilies, without a doubt, and we've
OL,17,Fgot to help these ex players."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
