OL,6,FMayor Burnham said: "The Football
OL,7,FGovernance Bill is going through the
OL,8,FHouse of Lords at the moment and it'll
OL,9,Fbe in the Commons in the spring.
OL,11,F"What we will do is bring together an
OL,12,Famendment to that bill that requires
OL,13,Ffootball to have a fully funded
OL,14,Fcompensation scheme to support former
OL,15,Fplayers in their families who are
OL,16,Fstruggling with dementia and other
OL,17,Fneuro degenerative conditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
