OL,3,CNobby Stiles 'sold medals to pay for
OL,4,Cdementia care'
OL,6,F"We will launch a campaign in
OL,7,Fparliament in the spring for
OL,8,Famendments be made so the football
OL,9,Fgame takes care of an issue that isn't
OL,10,Fresolved as of yet."
OL,12,FSpeaking after the meeting on Friday
OL,13,Fin Manchester, Mayor Andy Burnham said
OL,14,Fhe hopes the discussion will help
OL,15,Fbring about an amendment to the
OL,16,FFootball Governance Bill.
OL,18,FThe Premier League and PFA have a
OL,19,Fconfirmed an increase to funding to
OL,20,Fthe Football Brain Health Fund beyond
OL,21,Fits initial commitment of #1million.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
