OL,6,FThe PFA also offers a dedicated
OL,7,Fsupport team, which offers
OL,8,Fpersonalised guidance to players and
OL,9,Ffamilies, and provides free and
OL,10,Fconfidential access to dementia
OL,11,Fclinics and specialised Admiral Nurses.
OL,13,FPlayer education sessions on brain
OL,14,Fhealth risks are also offered to
OL,15,Fcurrent players by Astle and others,
OL,16,Fwhile the union continues to lobby at
OL,17,Fthe global level for the introduction
OL,18,Fof temporary concussion substitutes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
