OL,6,FThe FA co-funded the FIELD Study with
OL,7,Fthe PFA, which found that footballers
OL,8,Fwere three and a half times more
OL,9,Flikely to die of neurodegenerative
OL,10,Fdisease than age-matched members of
OL,11,Fthe general population.
OL,13,FThe latest FIELD update in December
OL,14,F2024 found the heightened risk among
OL,15,Ffootballers' was not driven by general
OL,16,Fhealth and lifestyle factors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
