OL,6,FWhile it will likely take long-term
OL,7,Fstudies to definitively link repeated
OL,8,Fheading to an increased risk of
OL,9,Fdeveloping neurodegenerative disease,
OL,10,Fthe FA has taken steps to reduce the
OL,11,Frisk in any case and is phasing out
OL,12,Fall heading in youth football up to
OL,13,Funder-11s by 2026.
OL,15,FA limit of 10 'high force' headers in
OL,16,Ftraining per week has been imposed in
OL,17,Fadult football from the professional
OL,18,Fgame down to grassroots.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
