OL,6,FAn FA spokesperson said: "We continue
OL,7,Fto take a leading role in reviewing
OL,8,Fand improving the safety of our game.
OL,10,F"This includes investing in and
OL,11,Fsupporting multiple projects in order
OL,12,Fto gain a greater understanding of
OL,13,Fthis area through objective, robust
OL,14,Fand thorough research.
