OL,6,F"We have already taken many proactive
OL,7,Fsteps to review and address potential
OL,8,Frisk factors which may be associated
OL,9,Fwith football whilst ongoing research
OL,10,Fcontinues in this area, including
OL,11,Fliaising with the international
OL,12,Fgoverning bodies."
OL,14,FThe Stiles family is also part of a
OL,15,Fgroup which is taking legal action
OL,16,Fagainst the FA, the EFL and the
OL,17,FInternational Football Association
OL,18,FBoard (IFAB), claiming they did not do
OL,19,Fenough to protect players from the
OL,20,Frisk of brain injuries.
